title: Andy Buroker '84 Joins Faegre Baker Daniels as Partner (DePauw University)
text: ( Source : DePauw University ) October 14 , 2015 Andy Buroker, a 1984 graduate of DePauw University, has joined Faegre Baker Daniels ' national real estate practice as a partner. He is based in the firm's Indianapolis north side office. 'Buroker
